quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  22,1,Yā 'Ayyuhā An-Nāsu Attaqū Rabbakum 'Inna Zalzalata As-Sā`ati Shay'un `Ažīmun
  22,2,Yawma Tarawnahā Tadh/halu Kullu Murđi`atin `Ammā 'Arđa`at Wa Tađa`u Kullu Dhāti Ĥamlin Ĥamlahā Wa Tará An-Nāsa Sukārá Wa Mā Hum Bisukārá Wa Lakinna `Adhāba Allāhi Shadīdun
  22,3,Wa Mina An-Nāsi Man Yujādilu Fī Allāhi Bighayri `Ilmin Wa Yattabi`u Kulla Shayţānin Marīdin
  22,4,Kutiba `Alayhi 'Annahu Man Tawallāhu Fa'annahu Yuđilluhu Wa Yahdīhi 'Ilá `Adhābi As-Sa`īri
  22,5,Yā 'Ayyuhā An-Nāsu 'In Kuntum Fī Raybin Mina Al-Ba`thi Fa'innā Khalaqnākum Min Turābin Thumma Min Nuţfatin Thumma Min `Alaqatin Thumma Min Muđghatin Mukhallaqatin Wa Ghayri Mukhallaqatin Linubayyina Lakum Wa Nuqirru Fī Al-'Arĥāmi Mā Nashā'u 'Ilá 'Ajalin Musammáan Thumma Nukhrijukum Ţiflāan Thumma Litablughū 'Ashuddakum Wa Minkum Man Yutawaffá Wa Minkum Man Yuraddu 'Ilá 'Ardhali Al-`Umuri Likaylā Ya`lama Min Ba`di `Ilmin Shay'āan Wa Tará Al-'Arđa Hāmidatan Fa'idhā 'Anzalnā `Alayhā Al-Mā'a Ahtazzat Wa Rabat Wa 'Anbatat Min Kulli Zawjin Bahījin
  22,6,Dhālika Bi'anna Allāha Huwa Al-Ĥaqqu Wa 'Annahu Yuĥyī Al-Mawtá Wa 'Annahu `Alá Kulli Shay'in Qadīrun
  22,7,Wa 'Anna As-Sā`ata 'Ātiyatun Lā Rayba Fīhā Wa 'Anna Allāha Yab`athu Man Fī Al-Qubūri
  22,8,Wa Mina An-Nāsi Man Yujādilu Fī Allāhi Bighayri `Ilmin Wa Lā Hudáan Wa Lā Kitābin Munīrin
  22,9,Thāniya `Iţfihi Liyuđilla `An Sabīli Allāhi Lahu Fī Ad-Dunyā Khizyun Wa Nudhīquhu Yawma Al-Qiyāmati `Adhāba Al-Ĥarīqi
  22,10,Dhālika Bimā Qaddamat Yadāka Wa 'Anna Allāha Laysa Bižallāmin Lil`abīdi